ğŸ”¹ Hasse Diagram (VERY IMPORTANT)

A Hasse diagram is a simplified graphical representation of a POSET.

Rules:

Draw elements as nodes

Draw edge a â†’ b if:

a < b

No intermediate element exists

Remove self-loops & transitive edges

Higher elements drawn upward

ğŸ“Œ GATE Favorite:
