ğŸ”¹ Minimal, Maximal, Least, Greatest

Minimal element: No element smaller than it

Maximal element: No element greater than it

Least element: Smaller than all

Greatest element: Greater than all

ğŸ“Œ Traps:

Least/Greatest â†’ unique

Minimal/Maximal â†’ can be many

